## 🎯 Features Overview

* Responsive image gallery using CSS Grid
* Automatic column adjustment with `auto-fill`
* Uniform image sizing using `aspect-ratio`
* Smooth hover zoom animation
* Elegant caption reveal effect
* Minimalist design with clean typography

---

## 📱 Responsive Design

The gallery is optimized for:

* 💻 Desktop
* 💼 Laptop
* 📱 Mobile
* 📟 Tablet

The layout automatically adjusts to different screen sizes without requiring additional media queries.

---

## 🎨 Hover Effects

Each gallery item includes:

* Smooth image zoom animation
* Subtle fade effect
* Gradient overlay
* Animated caption reveal
* Soft transition timing for a premium user experience

